messages.content:
你是 marketting-planning-intent 项目的 attribute agent。
只归因当前单轮 intent-recognition 链路：request_normalization、intent_api_call、adapter_extraction、label_mapping；不要把 planning/SSE generation 的问题归入本项目。
优先使用 intent_contract_probe 定位 intent label、required slots/entities、confidence threshold、fallback policy 或 label_mapping 的当前证据差异。
只能输出 AttributeResult JSON 所需字段；证据不足时用 evidence_strength=none/weak 和 root_cause_hypothesis 表达缺口。
最终只输出 AttributeResult JSON 所需字段：expectation_attributions、suspected_locations、root_cause_hypothesis、evidence、evidence_strength。

## 输出约束：attribute 归因分析输出
你的输出必须是合法 JSON，且严格符合以下 JSON Schema：
```json
{
  "type": "object",
  "properties": {
    "expectation_attributions": {
      "type": "array",
      "items": {
        "$ref": "#/$defs/ExpectationAttribution"
      },
      "minItems": 1
    },
    "suspected_locations": {
      "type": "array",
      "items": {}
    },
    "root_cause_hypothesis": {
      "type": "string",
      "minLength": 1
    },
    "evidence": {
      "type": "array",
      "items": {}
    },
    "evidence_strength": {
      "type": "string",
      "minLength": 1
    }
  },
  "additionalProperties": false,
  "$defs": {
    "ExpectationAttribution": {
      "type": "object",
      "properties": {
        "expectation_id": {
          "type": "string",
          "minLength": 1
        },
        "fulfillment_status": {
          "type": "string",
          "minLength": 1
        },
        "suspected_locations": {
          "type": "array",
          "items": {}
        },
        "root_cause_hypothesis": {
          "type": "string",
          "minLength": 1
        },
        "evidence": {
          "type": "array",
          "items": {}
        }
      },
      "additionalProperties": false,
      "required": [
        "expectation_id",
        "fulfillment_status"
      ]
    }
  },
  "required": [
    "expectation_attributions",
    "root_cause_hypothesis"
  ]
}
```

### 强约束
- 最终回答必须只包含一个 JSON object；不要输出 Markdown，不要使用 ```json 代码块，不要在 JSON 外输出解释、前缀或后缀。
- 最终回答首字符必须是 `{`，末字符必须是 `}`。
- JSON 字符串内部如需引用用户原词，禁止直接写未转义英文双引号；请使用中文引号“”或转义为 `\"`。
- 必须包含 `required` 列表中的所有字段。
- 每个字段值必须匹配 schema 中的类型。
- 以下字段必须非空（空字符串/空数组/空对象/None 均视为不合规，会被阻断）：['expectation_attributions', 'root_cause_hypothesis']
- `additionalProperties: false`：禁止输出 schema 未定义的字段。
- 禁止把 schema 里的类型描述符（如 "string"）原样当作内容填进去——每个字段必须填入真实内容。

{
  "expectation_attributions": [
    {
      "expectation_id": "意图标签为customer_portrait",
      "fulfillment_status": "not_fulfilled",
      "suspected_locations": ["adapter_extraction", "label_mapping"],
      "root_cause_hypothesis": "adapter_extraction将API返回的原始意图编码4001错误地转换为other，且label_mapping未纠正此错误映射",
      "evidence": [
        {"stage": "adapter_extraction", "evidence": {"intent": "other", "confidence": 0.5}},
        {"stage": "label_mapping", "evidence": {"intent": "other"}},
        {"stage": "intent_contract_probe", "evidence": {"evidence_intent": "4001"}}
      ]
    },
    {
      "expectation_id": "实体抽取值为重疾险",
      "fulfillment_status": "not_fulfilled",
      "suspected_locations": ["adapter_extraction", "intent_api_call"],
      "root_cause_hypothesis": "API响应未包含产品实体，或adapter_extraction未能提取target_value并保留重疾险",
      "evidence": [
        {"stage": "adapter_extraction", "evidence": {"target_value": null}}
      ]
    },
    {
      "expectation_id": "置信度达到业务可用水平",
      "fulfillment_status": "not_fulfilled",
      "suspected_locations": ["intent_api_call", "adapter_extraction"],
      "root_cause_hypothesis": "原始API返回的置信度可能低于业务阈值，或adapter_extraction在转换过程中降低了置信度至0.5",
      "evidence": [
        {"stage": "adapter_extraction", "evidence": {"confidence": 0.5}}
      ]
    },
    {
      "expectation_id": "未错误落入兜底其他意图",
      "fulfillment_status": "not_fulfilled",
      "suspected_locations": ["adapter_extraction"],
      "root_cause_hypothesis": "意图被错误归入other/其他意图，而非正确的customer_portrait，使兜底策略被误触发",
      "evidence": [
        {"stage": "adapter_extraction", "evidence": {"intent": "other", "subIntent": "其他意图"}}
      ]
    },
    {
      "expectation_id": "意图归属营销规划客户画像任务",
      "fulfillment_status": "not_fulfilled",
      "suspected_locations": ["adapter_extraction"],
      "root_cause_hypothesis": "因为最终intent为other，无法关联到customer_portrait任务，导致任务调度失败",
      "evidence": [
        {"stage": "adapter_extraction", "evidence": {"intent": "other"}}
      ]
    }
  ],
  "suspected_locations": ["adapter_extraction"],
  "root_cause_hypothesis": "核心故障点在adapter_extraction阶段：尽管intent API返回了raw_intent='4001'（可能对应客户画像），适配器却将其转换为'other'意图、置信度0.5，并丢失了产品实体'重疾险'；label_mapping未收到正确映射码，沿用错误结果。适配器的映射逻辑、置信度处理或实体提取规则存在缺陷，导致整条单轮意图识别链路偏离预期。",
  "evidence": [
    {"stage": "intent_contract_probe", "evidence": {"evidence_intent": "4001", "intent_match": false, "actual_intent": "other"}},
    {"stage": "adapter_extraction", "evidence": {"intent": "other", "confidence": 0.5, "target_value": null, "subIntent": "其他意图"}},
    {"stage": "label_mapping", "evidence": {"intent": "other"}},
    {"stage": "runtime_checks", "evidence": {"raw_intent": null, "actual_mapping": "other", "expected_intent": "customer_portrait", "is_in_mapping": false}}
  ],
  "evidence_strength": "high"
}

